		gravitational-wave observatory: Cosmic Explorer. With ten times the
		sensitivity of Advanced LIGO, Cosmic Explorer will push gravitational-wave
		astronomy towards the edge of the observable universe (\$z
		{\textbackslash}sim 100\$). The goals of this Horizon Study are to describe
		and evaluate design concepts for Cosmic Explorer; to plan for the United
		States' leadership in gravitational-wave astronomy; and to envisage the role
